## ğŸ“– About the Project

This project focuses on early prediction of forest fires by analyzing environmental data using machine learning algorithms. The aim is to assist in rapid response and prevention efforts by identifying fire risks before they become uncontrollable.

---

## âœ¨ Features

- âœ… Data preprocessing and cleaning
- âœ… Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- âœ… Training with multiple ML models (e.g., Logistic Regression, Random Forest)
- âœ… Evaluation with metrics (Accuracy, Precision, Recall, F1 Score)
- âœ… Visualizations and charts for insights
- âœ… Modular and clean project structure

